<li class="link tell_friend"><a href="https://www.dreamwidth.org/tools/tellafriend?journal=transitional_writes&amp;itemid=46365" ><img border='0' width="16" height="16" alt="Share This Entry" title="Share This Entry" src="https://www.dreamwidth.org/img/silk/entry/tellafriend.png"  /></a></li>
</ul></div>
</div>
